Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Elf Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:47.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- So many smells!\N- Reservation under Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,For the original blend\Ntasting experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:59.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the kind of tea you'd like,\Nand pick out your leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:05.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tea do\Nyou like, Tonome-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:08.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to focus on\Nthe effects they advertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:11.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Teas that improve your focus\Nor help you to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about you?\N- Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:21.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I really loved the one\Nyou made for me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:23.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I came up with that blend myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boy here came by the shop before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "I want something\Nthat'll make my girl happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lucky gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, spill! What's it feel like\Nto date an invisible man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been dating long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it serious? You guys cohabiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say we're\Nofficially dating just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just yet{\i0}, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's going to happen soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe tonight's the big night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ow!\N- Please excuse my idiot husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being oppressed by a white elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down, dark elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. That was a bit awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:20.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to make a tea blend for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:27.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make one for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it worth the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally made this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Check that ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll brew tea from\Nthe blends you created.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't putting the tea together fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I look forward to drinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:54.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find this shop just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do research for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I got carried away speculating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right on the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:14.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a habit of trying\Nto work out people's motivations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You have excellent intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fantastic quality\Nin a detective's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,About you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine what you look like\Nunless I touch you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- My hand, of course.\N- Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingers are more slender\Nthan my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are well kept, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:53.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people can't see them,\NI try to maintain good hygiene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:58.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see how well\Nkept they are for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see mine either, so I'm always\Nworried that they might look strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are very well kept too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like he's the one{\i0}\N{\i1}who can see right through {\i0}me{\i1}...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This was brewed\Nfrom the blends you created.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's try them.\N- O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Jarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,How does Tonome-san usually dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He wears suits most\Nof the time, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What are his suits like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What subset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Subset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... the English gentleman kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleman! That sounds very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it totally is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,English gentlemen are spies,\Nand that's super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,English gentlemen are spies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,She's talking about movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course Tonome\Nwears suits for his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was thinking of buying clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted information for reference...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're buying clothes for yourself,\Nwhy are you asking about Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You two want to go twinsies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants an outfit\Nfor their dates, you dumb feline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- What was that?!\N- Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's for... dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,With Tonome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I get you, Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressin' up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we please keep this between us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones\Nwho work here, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:53.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been buying the same kinds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,of outfits so I didn't end up\Nwith mismatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:01.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I want special clothing\Nfor special days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your shopping buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be pretty overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push Yako around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're short-tempered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:32.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You usually go girlish\Nand casual with your outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be handy to have some more mature
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,things you can wear\Nto high-class restaurants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Try this one on too!\N- W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confirm what\Nkind of outfit it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:46.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Image captured. Cloth is pale blue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Pale blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka. I'll describe it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This blouse is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a lively fabric...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "lively" mean in this context?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:08.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It flows just like hair,\Nwhich makes it seem really dynamic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I haven't been\Nvery considerate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about what\NKikira-san said to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I also almost made you trip\Nover my bike before, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Jarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your stomach bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat things off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:37.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can throw shade too, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:39.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:44.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! When we're done shopping,\NI'll take you to my favorite spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, Kikira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any restaurants you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, indulge me\Nin a little conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping for some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.75,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,KIKIRA-SAN\NRESTAURANT RECS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:24.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me\Nyour expressions, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lookie here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the teahouse owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Karma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,His wife, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a couple of elf spouses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.33,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,WAITING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsavory characters in white hoods?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:56.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They sit in a car across the street\Nfrom the shop every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been asking around\Nthe neighborhood about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and taking pictures from the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That does sound quite unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:07.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, in all my hundred years,\NI've never had a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... you {\i1}are{\i0} frightened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be following\Nus around as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did they follow you he—\N- No worries! We totally lost them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope he's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into the suspects\Nand think up countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Tonome.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I traced the transmitter\NJarashi stuck on the car
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,to a big pharma corp in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the people in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,they dress all the same,\Nbut their faces are all different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be pretty dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be an organized thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond simple stalking, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Jarashi-san's guarding\Nthem. Let her know—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome, bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple of cars stopped\Nin front of the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and a bunch of men marched out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:12.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the lovebirds out the back way,\Nand we're on the run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome! It's just like a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to be panicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There's multiple threats.\NI'll head that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-san, hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please let them work it out safely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm afraid it's past the\Ntime we accept new clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized they might target the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A white elf, just like my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my father. He runs\Na pharmaceutical company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:28.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You got worried about your\Ndaughter and wanted to check in on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, why is the whole clan involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And in disguises, at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:38.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they all wanted to come,\Nand we didn't want you to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you two visited a detective agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,so we thought there might be\Na misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So they did follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:49.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, Daddy! Clumsy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:56.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep in mind, I still haven't\Ngiven you my blessing, dark elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:01.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta say, I never asked for it, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you say that's... case closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of ongoing issues,\Nbut they're all on their end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done today, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have a drinking party\Nwith my co-workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had many\Nchances for it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I just like to get home on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sourpuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't get any girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a partner,\Nso I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:50.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been wondering.\NShizuka, you don't drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:54.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but it's harder\Nto get home if I'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be dangerous\Nif I dull my senses too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll walk you home\Nthis time. Feel free to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is there anything nice and sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Jarashi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- What now?{\i0}\N- Yako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:29.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called you a taxi.\NI'll make sure you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-Wh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I invite him up for tea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:42.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But is my room even{\i0}\N{\i1}in any condition for company?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yako-san.\N- Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a restaurant I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we go there sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's a dark restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat in a pitch-black interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I've heard of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:15:00.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been interested in seeing\Nthe world you live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:04.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you think?\N- The world I live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be your guide through the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for seeing me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to share a cup of tea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave the taxi waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd like, I'll happily\Ncome back again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:41.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good night.\N- Good... night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I've gotta get someone{\i0}\N{\i1}to review my room for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yako-san?\N- Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing another\Nbeautiful outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll guide me through the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Tonome-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you not see anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:18.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's\Na very faint light right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now put out all the lights
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and plunge you into true darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it pitch black now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome-san, welcome to my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:52.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you'll want to pat around\Nand find out where everything is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tonome-san sounds really nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try this "terrine" stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I need to freshen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that all right?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to cut it short\Nafter inviting you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We wasted the wonderful food, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:03.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the staff to box it up for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:11.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't wait to get back and eat it!\N- Neither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:15.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come by my place to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I arranged it all on one plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:38.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so nervous, all I can say is "Oh!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-san. I'm sorry\Nabout the trouble today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it, but\NI may be afraid of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I can think of is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how they sometimes\Nhold sleepaway camp for children?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this time when they\Nhosted a test of courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to hold a candle\Nand walk up a mountain road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kat-chan's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Kat-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be dangerous to go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to wait\Nuntil someone came to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:51.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up on waiting and managed\Nto make it back to the cabins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody even realized I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:03.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm invisible, it's all\Nthe same to them if I'm there or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was\Na little traumatic for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,In the city, you're\Nrarely in the total dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized it\Nmade me uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,so it really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be careful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonome-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I notice these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sounds are usually so put-together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's easy to tell\Nwhen they're flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, you're trying\Nto sound cheerful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:45.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds of your glass and the\Nrate you're drinking are all scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you were really scared and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:54.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd miss you if you weren't there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd definitely look for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:10.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that your reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a problem with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:23.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized I like having you nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:32.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're officially dating now,\Nthen what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on dropping you off\Nand coming straight home this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,"This time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-san, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want me to do something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You're\Nspeaking in sound effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the sound\Nof being mentally unprepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:00.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Squeak!\N- I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't squeak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.88,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 2: THE GREAT DATE PLAN\NTO BE CONTINUED
""";

