Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.26,Main,Morimo,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.41,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hey, Morimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.32,Main,Mini,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:36.88,Main,Morimo,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.52,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hey, Mini! 'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.80,Main,Mini,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.19,Main,Morimo,0,0,0,,Goofing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.76,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.16,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.23,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,That's so creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.48,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,No one asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.68,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,Move or I'll crush those hair buns of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:32.64,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.49,Main,Suzuki's mom,0,0,0,,If you two don't hurry up, you'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:37.49,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:57.41,Main,Azuma,0,0,0,,Morning, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.80,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh, Azuma! Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.84,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,You and Taira came together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.89,Main,Taira,0,0,0,,We did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.65,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Morning, Nabesato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:03.89,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:03.89,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.66,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Hey there, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.65,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.83,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh! T-Tani-kun! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:14.76,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:19.72,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you're so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.66,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Proper greetings will save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.64,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Hey, my eyelashes look good today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.79,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.90,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Why not just use false eyelashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:34.67,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I could, but I prefer my real eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:39.78,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And the mascara comes off \Nif you sweat, cry, or rub it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:43.18,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,So, I just end up wondering \Nwhich brand I should try...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.19,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.91,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.94,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know anything about it, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.45,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun! You're icy as always today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.21,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Why do you get such a kick \Nout of pestering Tani-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.03,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,about things he obviously has no interest in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.96,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:06.02,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I love the way he shuts me down. \NI can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:10.08,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,If you ever need help \Npicking mascara, I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.05,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.26,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Shut down again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.71,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,He's ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.47,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Stop bothering Tani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:25.56,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, I'm so sorry. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.81,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.16,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I'm desperately in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:49.21,Basic Sign,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,115)\fnArial}YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.58,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Did you finish your English homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.00,Main,Waanabe,0,0,0,,I only did the parts \NI thought I might get right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.41,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Do the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.04,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Sitting in the seat next to mine is Tani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:18.63,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,He seems like a quiet guy \Nwith glasses to everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Main,text,0,0,0,,{\b1\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\an4}GROUP ASSIGNMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Main,text,0,0,0,,{\b1\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\an4}ANALYZE GEOGRAPHIC CHALLENGES \NIN OUR TOWN AND MAKE PROPOSALS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Main,text,0,0,0,,{\b1\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\an4}TERRAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Main,text; top to bottom,0,0,0,,{\b1\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\an4}ROADS -> CREATE TOURIST ATTRACTIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.01,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,but Tani-kun speaks his mind clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.01,Main,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\an7\b1\c&HE8FDE1&\3c&HAE7527&\shad0\fs28\fad(318,1)}THWACK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.06,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,The teacher will probably flag \Nthis part, so it needs to be redone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.52,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Huh? Why? Good enough is good enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.73,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,And he has the same attitude \Nno matter who he's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.81,Onscreen,text; top,0,0,0,,HE'S NOT PUSHY, THOUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.56,Main,text; vertical; sfx,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HEDDEBC&\3c&HA8752C&\shad0\frz-69\pos(350,180)\fad(565,470)}FWIP...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.98,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Do you have your assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:39.65,Onscreen,text; top,0,0,0,,{\fad(271,1)\pos(360,85)}HE DOESN'T GROVEL, EITHER
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.57,Main,text; vertical; sfx,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HF7E4C9&\3c&H87745F&\shad0\frz-99\pos(210,120)\fad(521,477)}FWIP...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.69,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.07,Main,Morimo,0,0,0,,Thanks for collecting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.36,Main,Azuma,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.78,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Like the last time we changed seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.53,Main,text; top,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\pos(440,75)\frz4\fad(357,10)}FRONT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.53,Main,text; bottom,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9A773D&\fnArial\fs16\bord2\shad0\pos(440,333)\frz3\fad(277,10)}BACK
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.78,Flashback,teacher,0,0,0,,Okay. Change seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.42,Main,text,0,0,0,,{\fs32\b1\pos(320,240)\c&H6FD5EC&\3c&H66B1CF&\shad0}A MIRACLE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:57.92,Flashback Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I'm right next to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.80,Flashback Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,This is crazy. What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.76,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I hope you'll treat me well, neighbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:05.68,Main,text; horizontal,0,0,0,,{\b1\fad(569,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs32\shad0\bord3\c&H65296F&\3c&HC2E2FB&\pos(70,250)}TENSE...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:05.68,Main,text; vertical,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs32\shad0\bord3\b1\c&HBAB7F0&\3c&H591E4F&\frz-50\pos(50,170)}SMILE...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.18,Flashback,Tani,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.85,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,The thing about being in the front row...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:10.93,Onscreen,text,0,0,0,,{\fad(487,1)\fnArial\an4\pos(220,55)}( {\i1}Trying to make small talk \N\h\h\hwith relatable anecdotes{\i0} )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.93,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,The blackboard can be harder \Nto read that you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.94,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I'll read anything you can't make out, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.73,Flashback,Tani,0,0,0,,I think I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.82,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.90,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Tani-kun doesn't adjust his \Nbehavior without good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:27.03,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I just really... \Nreally admire that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.03,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Suzuki, which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.41,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Sorry, I wasn't listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.20,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.25,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,B-But, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.50,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I think that a person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.46,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,would rev up the crowd better \Nthan an audio recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.88,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Right, Tani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.46,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.47,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, if she's bothering you, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.68,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.77,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,See? He says it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.48,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Whew! What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.48,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\c&HD3D79D&\3c&H75733B&\bord2\pos(270,245)\frz20}WHEW
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.02,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, I'm sorry!\N I love you, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.28,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you normally, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.24,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I'm always worrying about how others see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.99,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,so I can't talk in a way \Nthat reveals that I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.33,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I admire Tani-kun so much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.87,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,you and I are polar opposites!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.33,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Right! After school, let's all go to KingBurg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.00,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzuki! You'll come, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.01,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I have to do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.51,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs28\an2\c&HD2B0F5&\3c&H614E2D&}EXCITED\NEXCITED\NEXCITED
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.47,Main - Top,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I'm totally going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.85,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,330)\fs28\fad(274,474)\c&HB9E9F6&\3c&H8F4EEA&}YAAAAAAAAAY
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.35,Main - Top,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:37.27,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Suzuki, will you let me copy your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.73,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.81,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.86,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh, fine. You're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.15,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.43,Main,girl A,0,0,0,,Oh, Suzuki! Your story \Nyesterday made me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.66,Main,girl B,0,0,0,,Suzuki-san, do you mind \Nif I follow your account, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.12,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I didn't post anything weird, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.75,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Sure! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.54,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.83,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Tani's really smart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.55,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the group work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.80,Main,Taira,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \NI saw him heading to cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.55,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Huh? Is he headed for UTokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.97,Main,Taira,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.18,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,He's really amazing, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:14.22,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,He lives in a different \Nworld from the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.31,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Don't lump me in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.27,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Suzuki's the closest to \NTani-kun in our group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.61,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,What? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.98,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,That's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.07,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.95,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I'm just at an age when stuff \Ncatches in my throat easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.07,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,You're too young for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.58,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Oh! SudaKen won Most Beloved \NActor for a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.58,Main,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,250)\frz-10\fs32\fnArial\b1\i1\shad3\bord2\c&HDCA0F8&\3c&HE13B62&\4c&HE13B62&}SUDAKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.58,Onscreen,text; either side of character,0,0,0,,{\fs24\c&H635255&\frz15\pos(400,80)}QUIRKY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.58,Onscreen,text; either side of character,0,0,0,,{\fs24\c&H635255&\frz-20\pos(600,95)}ACTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.41,Main,Taira,0,0,0,,Girls really like the mischievous types, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.17,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Whoa. SudaKen's the only one \Nwho's boyfriend material.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.59,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,There it is! Suzuki's stanning SudaKen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.68,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Some say reading the room \Nis for other people's sakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.97,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,but it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.77,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I do it completely for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.69,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.80,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,sometimes it tires me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.07,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.58,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.01,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,T-Tani-kun, are you heading \Nhome now? It's late, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.02,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I know my face must've \Nlooked hideous just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.02,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,There was committee work to be submitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:45.27,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, what way do you take home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.69,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Out the gate and turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.28,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.53,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,No one's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.53,Main,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs18\b1\fnArial\c&HDABEF5&\3c&H857A7C&\shad0\pos(400,130)}GLANCE GLANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.03,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.53,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.12,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Want to go part of the way home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.00,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,My heart's gonna burst out of my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.67,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,So, Tani-kun, your house is this way, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.05,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,We've never ended up together before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.76,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.19,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm always running around \Ngoofing off after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.73,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,No wonder I never saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.23,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And you have student council \Nstuff to do too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.73,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.95,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And, um, we went to KingBurg the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.71,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,and the burger was huge!\NIt didn't even fit in the bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.34,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,The buns were basically \Nserved on the side, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.00,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I had no idea how to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.97,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Wait. Is this topic interesting at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.60,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.60,Onscreen,text,0,0,0,,{\fs18\c&H7512E3&\4c&H83EBFC&\bord3\frz10\pos(560,180)}A QUESTION!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.18,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was! Super good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:03.56,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I know! Tani-kun, want to grab one with me? Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.06,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.11,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.57,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,What did he just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.36,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Is he just being polite?\NOr matching the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.87,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,No, Tani-kun isn't that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.50,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Find something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.00,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Say something back to him, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.76,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:39.22,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding so hard! I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.51,Main,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\b1\fnArial\c&HE5FFC1&\bord1\shad2\3c&H9E9F2C&\4c&H9E9F2C&\an8}BONK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.22,Main,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,395)\fs28\b1\fnArial\c&H9AFFF8&\bord2\shad0\3c&H694BA6&\4c&H9E9F2C&\pos(440,60)}SHOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.31,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Uh, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.63,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.43,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.10,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:28.94,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,What? What do I do?\N Right now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.86,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I'm certain my hand is sweating like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:38.28,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,My heartbeat is so loud \NI can hear it pounding in my ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.32,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Am I dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:56.34,Onscreen,text; bubble; Tani,0,0,0,,{\an9}I'm this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:59.38,Onscreen,text; bottom,0,0,0,,{\fad(816,971)\an2\c&HB9FCF8&\3c&H6A3889&\bord2}I think we probably said something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:58.26,Italics - Top,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I don't remember how I got home after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.34,Onscreen,text; bubble; Suzuki,0,0,0,,{\pos(100,70)\c&HA23CBE&}Oh! I'm going\Nthe other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.38,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\c&H884CEA&\fnArial\bord1\fs20\frz10\pos(200,230)\fad(439,971)}WHOOOOSH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.38,Onscreen,text; bubble; Suzuki,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,70)\c&HA23CBE&\bord1\fad(1,971)}Tani-kun,\Nsee you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.38,Onscreen,text; bubble; Tani,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(238,971)}Yeah. Later...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.30,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,I'm ho—!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.43,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs28\c&HCA8F63&\3c&H5F281C&\shad1\4c&H5F281C&\pos(390,80)\frz5\fad(773,1)}GLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.10,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,Don't lie down in the entryway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.43,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh. Nii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:14.36,Onscreen,text; squiggly line,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(550,80)\c&HB1F4F9&\3c&H7A53B6&\bord2\frz-27\fad(235,436)}GYAAAAAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.27,Onscreen,text; either side of Suzuki,0,0,0,,{\fs24\fnArial\c&HD1B2F4&\3c&H6F316D&\pos(350,250)\fad(1,388)}FLAIL\N\h\h\h\h\h\hFLAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.23,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:18.15,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(200,10)\fad(897,389)\c&HA2DDF7&\3c&H8E80EB&\bord2}DAZED...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:18.07,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,We... held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.36,Main,Suzuki's mom,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.20,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna eat, then gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.41,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.70,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,he grabbed my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.16,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,This is crazy! This is crazy! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.46,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,How do I face everyone at school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:35.71,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,My heart is racing so fast! \NI'll never get to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.76,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\pos(220,20)\fs24\c&HC9A2F4&\3c&H6F2A51&\fad(1571,436)}AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.17,Main,Suzuki's brother,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:44.26,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs24\c&HCBFCFA&\3c&H713332&\bord2\pos(500,150)\fad(236,932)\frz-70}SNORE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.97,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs24\c&H64242E&\3c&HFCC3F4&\bord2\pos(240,250)\fad(237,1)\frz-51}ZZZZZZZZZZZZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.52,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(400,180)\frz-40\fad(229,1)\c&HAFFEF8&\3c&H8B13D9&\bord1\shad1\4c&H8B13D9&}THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.52,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.65,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.36,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Morning? You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.78,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Wait. What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.04,Onscreen,text,0,0,0,,{\fs28\fnArial\frz34\pos(460,195)\bord1\shad2\3c&H5D0472&\4c&H5D0472&\c&HC9A2F4&}TMP{\c&HD5CAF7&}TMP{\c&HC9A2F4&}TMP{\c&HD5CAF7&}TMP{\c&HC9A2F4&}TMP{\c&HD5CAF7&}TMP{\c&HC9A2F4&}TMP
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.04,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I didn't have any absences \Nor tardies yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.75,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.79,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.29,Onscreen,text; left to right,0,0,0,,{\fad(238,1)\frz30\c&H731593&\3c&HC8A5E2&\bord2}Everyone\h\h\h\h\N{\c&H7A5F53&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\pos(150,200)}Brother   Mom   Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.29,Onscreen,text; note,0,0,0,,{\frz-5\fs14\pos(390,250)\bord1\fad(988,1)}It's all right to be \Nlate sometimes,\Nbut make sure\Nyou eat breakfast.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:17.29,Onscreen,text; top,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fad(948,1)\fs32\pos(530,30)\c&HB3FDF8&\3c&HB64226&\bord2\shad1\4c&HB64226&}FOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.29,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.05,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And it's more like midday than morning now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.05,Onscreen,text; right,0,0,0,,{\fad(482,1)\pos(520,110)\bord2\fs24\frz-66\fnArial\c&HF7D2F6&\3c&H472164&}CALM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.05,Onscreen,text; ribbon,0,0,0,,{\fad(487,1)\pos(320,250)\3c&HC0FEF9&\bord2}Being ridiculously late\Nactually relaxes her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.05,Main - Top,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I get the feeling hurrying\N won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.14,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Let's microwave this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.56,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,It's already lunchtime, but good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.31,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Suzuki, it's rare for you to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.69,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You could've just taken \Nthe day off at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.98,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,But I want to do our \Nelective P.E. class, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.07,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.95,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Oh, Suzuki! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.20,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Yeah! 'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.53,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hey, are you and Tani dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.45,Onscreen,text,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs32\pos(320,40)\bord2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}HUH\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.49,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:56.50,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Gapacho said you two walked \Nhome together yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.83,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Who the heck is Gapacho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.59,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,It wasn't someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.25,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Gapacho's knows what he saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.46,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Not our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.22,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hang on, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.68,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.89,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,we're in the "might be mutual, \Nbut not yet confirmed" phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.97,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,The most delicate phase of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.56,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,It's not something you can poke at for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.48,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I'm playing for keeps here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.11,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,And, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.23,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,someone saw us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.23,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.03,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Saw us where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.03,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.42,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.29,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.05,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,That's my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.55,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Can I grab my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.64,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, sorry. I'll move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.68,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,It's fine. We go somewhere else next period.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.64,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.90,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,It couldn't be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.16,Main,teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}The body breaks down carbohydrates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:14.33,Main,teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}and blood sugar levels rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.66,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,He heard me denying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.50,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,It was so beyond rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.96,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,You have it all wrong! \NI didn't mean to say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.42,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.18,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,No, no, no! I could never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.39,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,But I want to apologize ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.97,Italics - Top,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.22,Main,text; sfx; left,0,0,0,,{\fad(147,309)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\c&HCAAFF1&\3c&H52558F&\shad0\frz-66\pos(290,300)\fad(146,187)}FWIP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.43,Onscreen,text; sfx; right,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,144)\bord1\frz-40\pos(590,260)\fad(1,104)\c&H4D4354&\3c&HBCD2DC&}DROP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.27,Italics - Top,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I hope Tani-kun doesn't feel awful right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.02,Main - Top,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.86,Main - Top,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you haven't \Npicked up any of the shuttles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:41.69,Main,text; sfx; left,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\c&HA4FFF8&\3c&H422D56&\shad0\frz-26\pos(220,230)\fad(143,273)}SHFF
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.23,Onscreen,text; sfx; right,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz49\pos(415,221)\fad(443,271)\c&H4D4354&\3c&HBCD2DC&}POING
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.19,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Just pick 'em up with your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:49.49,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,20)\fs24\shad2\c&HEAEEC0&\3c&H813827&\4c&H813827&\fad(570,226)}ANGST ANGST\NANGST ANGST
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:49.45,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Oh, why am I always so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.37,Main,classmate,0,0,0,,Sorry, Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:03.71,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fad(4443,1)\an1\c&HB45C27&\bord1\fs24\3c&HB45C27&}SWEAT\NSWEAT\NSWEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.25,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.83,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,I have to talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.54,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Hurry up and explain this misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.21,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,But... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.38,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Here, where everyone else is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.22,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.47,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H8C00D8&\i1\frz-70\fs24\pos(50,150)\fad(191,1)}BA-DUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.39,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,T-Tani-ku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.19,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Please forget what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.44,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:46.13,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Come on, Suzuki! This popcorn\Ncoupon expires today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.09,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hey, weren't you just talking to Tani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.67,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,You really do get along, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.13,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.64,Main,girl,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.14,Main,boy,0,0,0,,Do it again! Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:04.98,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.40,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,am in love with Tani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.19,Main,Yamada; Watanabe; Satou,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.57,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,It's a one-sided love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.40,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:19.34,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And yesterday... I invited him \Nto walk home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.75,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Is that... wrong somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.21,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.21,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.92,Onscreen,text; bubble,0,0,0,,{\fad(396,1)\pos(600,100)\fs20\c&H656360&\3c&HFBF5ED&\bord1}So loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.25,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,What? You should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.05,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Anyone would think you just \N met up on the way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:35.26,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Who would think it was a serious situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.55,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Huh? Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:42.43,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fad(817,1)\c&H71695D&\fs24\frz-23\pos(350,240)}GLOOOOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:40.56,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,I feel like I said something \Nmajorly insensitive at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.43,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,You're always insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:46.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,So, Tani-kun already left. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.19,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.94,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,You might make it if you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.94,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,This is major, Suzuki! Go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.66,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the popcorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.82,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Sorry! I really don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.58,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:04.00,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Run, Suzuki! Show us speed \Nthat won't shame your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.96,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You're a Suzuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.34,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,20)\fs24\bord2\c&HACFFF6&\3c&H7B5ED4&\fad(1,273)}SLOW\NSLOW\NSLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.55,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,How slow can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:13.92,Main,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hit 'im hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.97,Main,Satou,0,0,0,,Look ahead of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.80,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:20.89,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.98,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,Saying how I feel out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.77,Italics,Suzuki; internal,0,0,0,,was this easy to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:45.29,Italics - Top,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,I gave in to temptation.\NThat's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.62,Onscreen,text; bubble,0,0,0,,{\c&H94916C&\3c&HC1C198&\bord2\pos(200,200)\fad(528,1)}No use\Nregretting\Nit now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.38,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,Suzuki-san sits next to me. \NShe always talks to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.38,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,but she doesn't care about me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.13,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,It's just light banter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.18,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Want to go part of the way home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:02.97,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,That's what I thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.53,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.74,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,I thought she might not come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.08,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:30.17,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, I grew used to \NSuzuki-san talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.84,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,A day without her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.42,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.51,Italics,Tani; internal,0,0,0,,is just too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:42.68,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:56.19,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,T-Tani-kun, sorry that I pester you \Nwith stupid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:00.41,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry for what I said \Nin front of everyone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:04.28,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I didn't know how to talk to you, Tani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:09.71,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I was scared that everyone \Nwould see how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.38,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I'm a really pathetic human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.46,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:20.38,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Tani-kun, I want to spend more time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.72,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,When you held my hand, it made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:30.18,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,So happy that I couldn't sleep \Nlast night and overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.23,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,I mean, it's sort of like, \N"so you did sleep," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.74,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.82,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:47.91,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,When you're not talking, \NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:52.33,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,That's the kind of pathetic human being I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.38,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Would you... be all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.93,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,That face you're making is so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:04.89,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.76,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:10.98,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:11.77,Onscreen,text; sfx,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\frz-77\fs24\bord2\pos(400,100)\c&H84F3F7&\3c&H6C396F&}WAAAHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:15.36,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,I feel like I've made you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.77,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Well, that's because you actually did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.74,Main,Tani,0,0,0,,Mascara, was it? It'll come off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:29.79,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,You really were listening, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:33.46,Main,Suzuki,0,0,0,,This is crazy! My heart's all fluttery!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.25,Main - Top,Tani,0,0,0,,Huh? Why? What caused it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:36.08,Main - Top,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Oh, honestly!

""";

