Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you need a name to call me by,\Njust call me "Saber."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a classy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That sword you had...\NWhich drugstore did you find it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If what Francesca told us is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that guy would be King Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he swears to Arthur Pendragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Swearing to oneself is a strange tale indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the girl\Nthat seems to be the Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is honestly answering\Nthe questions we ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, she is quite fatigued...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems she has muddled memories\Ndue to hypnotic Magecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Other than the tattoos engraved onto her body\Nsimilar to Command Spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she is basically an ordinary citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this girl took the right\Nto be a Master for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she must be quite a skilled Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:01:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Perhaps one that was hastily prepared\Nand sent by an external faction?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Einzberns, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is intel that one of their homunculi\Nhas entered Snowfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there is a possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}that she hasn't had\Nmuch information shared with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let surveillance drop\Nfrom the girl or the Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, don't forget surveillance on Caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had a request from Sir Caster earlier.\NHe said, "Let me play in the casino."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Come on, man!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Denied. It'd be asinine\Nto have a Heroic Spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}galavanting around a casino\Nduring a Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All-in on red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A woman who seeks to use me should not cower\Nbefore anyone other than me, Tiné Chelc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I am terribly sorry, Sir Gilgamesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, this is the location where people and fortune\Ncome and go the most in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This amusement center uses currency\Nto create its own world for extravagant spending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,World, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A child should act as a child\Nand take in the sights with their eyes shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, everything about this world\Nmust pale in comparison to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But do not have blind faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If your eyes should shine as such,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you should also use them\Nto properly ascertain your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which way will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is regaining this land from those Mages\Na decision you have made...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or merely the words of a puppet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So long as my friend is present, I intend\Nto fully enjoy myself in this Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to wield me as a Servant\Nof your own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,be prepared to bare\Nall of what you keep within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All-in on black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go all-in on black, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to borrow some of your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta get started on the right track\Nsince I have a big job after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've stocked up on some luck thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return this fortune to your garden later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King Gilgamesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be so alarmed, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're no ordinary mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hansa Cervantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be supervising this Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I was getting carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, my spirit soared at being called upon\Nto such a magnificent stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got carried away and killed a man,\Nthen destroyed the Opera House?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did not murder that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you need to do is research how much\Nthe repairs on the Opera House shall cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you will let me know, I will reimburse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me a madman like you\Nhas some means to pay the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you can invest in me\Nas my patron if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never forget my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say for free, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you a magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! You'll be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have not moved one step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if I wanted to, I could have fled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or taken care of you all easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my way of demonstrating\Nmy respect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Respect, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not intend to stay in your custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to prove\Nthat the girl over there is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will disappear with the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I will comply with your restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be in your best interest to come up\Nwith an excuse for how you let me escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I can help you guys think of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he hasn't even a thought\Nof concealing the Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the memories\Nof the three inside through hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, you have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's claiming to be a priest from the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you a tourist? Where are you from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I assume you're Japanese?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'd better not be lying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you come here for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look rather fatigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my Spiritual Form,\NI can walk through walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The interrogation is on a break right now,\Nso I came by to see how you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you\Nto not meddle in my affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my Master, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your Master or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means I do not have to abide\Nby your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, I can meddle with you\Nto my heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will be taking care of you,\Nso brace yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be in a Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that may not work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because of the spell\Nplanted within your tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems a Magical Energy path...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has been connected with you instead of the Mage\Nthat originally had the Command Spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we may not be\Nin a Master-Servant relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we do share the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything about that—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, I cannot gain Magical Energy,\Nso I would have disappeared immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel indebted,\Ndon't get involved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I decline!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will look after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a venerable busybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cry all you wish in defiance,\Nbut I will save you in myriad ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Save me... from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other war participants, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, I'm not a Master—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you are a Master or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we are connected\Nthrough a path of Magical Energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you will naturally become a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off like this than being captured\Nby the enemy and executed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure go to extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you can call me "Saber."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}HE'S HOPELESS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel ashamed to not name myself\Nto my benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I will tell you my True Name in due time\Nwhen I see the right opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you let me know, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you in such a location?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that tattoo—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell me your name first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Chief Orlando Reeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hansa Cervantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Overseer dispatched\Nto Snowfield Central Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand if I phrase it that way,\Ndon't you, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to feign innocence despite the barrier\Nyou put up all around the police station, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just means there will be no place for you\Nto escape to after losing your Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means less work for me,\Nso it'd be a great help to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that you're a rogue\Nwho has nothing to do with the Clock Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}you've collected about 30 unnatural personnel\Nwithin the police organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite something\Nto have dug up all of that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you lot have already failed\Nat keeping the ritual a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, is that Servant and his Master here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are participants in the Holy Grail War\Nthat the Church has no information about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like to get over the greetings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this isn't something\Nto talk about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of jumping into the bowels\Nof a group still shrouded in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will acknowledge that caution...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but had you not thought that this lobby\Nwould already be within my bowels?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magecraft to clear out a crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much does the Church know right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your statements will never be brought to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've watched\Na few too many police dramas, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not wise to make the Church your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I assume I may be no match against you lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but bullying someone like me will put a crack\Nin the relationship between the organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed. I would prefer\Nthe amicable sharing of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be threatening a good Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will scream and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caster? How do you know this number—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'd better flee\Nfrom there right away, Brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or prepare to return fire at full strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somethin' real bad is heading to ya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My allies would enter\Nfrom the front or back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They even took out the emergency power supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Setting up spells for light sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your Servant just now, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're overstepping your role as Overseer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call it humble resistance against an authority\Nthat has threatened a weak, ordinary citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like someone unleashed\Na Noble Phantasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can use magic, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not magic. Magecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with,\Nthis isn't something that I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First and foremost,\NI'm going to take you to a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this cell the safest place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are barriers\Nset up all over this police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"It seems"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what's going on.\NIs there a Mage in the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Likely so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that vibration was another Servant attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell me things like that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that were the case, I would've sliced\Nthe door open and left immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just consider it as if I'm talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the ceiling of the cell we were just in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was a spell set up that could kill\Nthe person inside from hypoxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump in yet! We'll block\Nthe escape path! To your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're all... Noble Phantasms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the standard formula\Nis for Servants to wield Noble Phantasms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's the job of an author to destroy that formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All general staff have been evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A bounded field has been activated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to conceal at least some of the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skirt the night shadows...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:40.79,On Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SKIRT THE NIGHT SHADOWS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zabaniya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask for more for a touchstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you destroy the lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will suppress her at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Powers of a heretic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Expose the mirage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:20.25,On Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EXPOSE THE MIRAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zabaniya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're making the Magic Circuits go haywire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zabaniya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have multiple Noble Phantasms, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflow with agony...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zabaniya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Master must have\Nquite the stock of Magical Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of serving a Mage, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I seek not the Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will break apart the Holy Grail War\Nthat has led astray my great predecessors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should be long gone\Nfighting like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with no supply of Magical Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, marvelous! Just marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This mud-slinging brawl is much to my liking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of spellwork this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I had thought you were overreaching,\Nchallenging a Heroic Spirit as a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yet it actually looks\Nlike you're a pretty good match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there is even one Mage among you capable of\Ndetermining the characteristics of her Noble Phantasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you police may yet gain a chance of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you lot fight a good fight\Nand die off honorably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a great scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, if I rip off his other hand,\Nwill his show of pain be even better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your squealing. How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely a masterpiece,\Nworthy of being called a "Noble Phantasm."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A toy too good for human hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O my beloved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Jester Karture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As your Master, I will affirm\Neverything about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and as an inhuman Dead Apostle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:04.83,On Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DEAD APOSTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I will take everything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Dead Apostle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Dead Apostle? We have a Dead Apostle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A vampire? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting even more interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is a bit bad for my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back there, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This heart still remembers the feeling\Nof your palm! Like that of an intense kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It literally took hold of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've received Magical Energy\Nfrom a monster like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Apostle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I order you with a Command Spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Transport to a location\Nas far away from this city as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The baton has been passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just die already,\Nyou bags of blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clan Calatin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm more powerful\Nthan a Heroic Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, a Heroic Spirit\Nis something that affirms human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It protects the rules of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, we Dead Apostles deny human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've existed in violation of all your rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is simply an issue of compatibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be a different story, even with the same Noble\NPhantasm, if a Servant were the one wielding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what all of you are lacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Invaluableness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lot have not one bit of faith\Nin a higher being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not in gods, not even in Heroic Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you don't even believe\Nin your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you want to rely on tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no invaluableness in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot teach you\Nthe concept of invaluableness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I can teach you evanescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I will take this, not even a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll crush the head of this so-called Chief\Nthat all of you put your trust in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to at the very least\Nfight back as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What useless resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not one thing will reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not one thing will reach you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My coffee got you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.93,On Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EPISODE 2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,didn't it?

""";

